<h1><i class="fa fa-newspaper"></i>Sharing by News Post</h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><a href="#help"><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>Help</a></li>
	<li><a href="#help/sharing-files"><i class="fa fa-share"></i>Sharing Files</a></li>
	<li><i class="fa fa-newspaper"></i>Sharing by News Post</li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<p><%= application.name %> allows the ability to share items by post.  This attaches files and folders to be shared to news posts.  Since your news posts can be public or private, this allows you to share items with the public or only with your friends. </p>

	<ol>
		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-newspaper"></i>Sharing Items by News Post</h2>
			<p>To share items by post, select the files or folders that you would like to share and then click "By News Post" on the Share menu. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="dropdown menu" src="images/help/sharing-files/sharing-by-post/share-by-post-menu-item@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">"By News Post" on the Share Menu</div>
			</div>

			<p>This will launch the <a href="#apps/topic-viewer">News Browser</a> app where you can add a message to your news post and specify whether you would like this post to be visible to friends only or public. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/sharing-files/sharing-by-post/share-by-post.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Share by News Post"><img src="images/help/sharing-files/sharing-by-post/share-by-post.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Share by News Post</div>
			</div>

			<p>After typing your message and hitting the "Post" button, your files or images will be posted to your news feed for your friends to see. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/sharing-files/sharing-by-post/post-with-gallery.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Post with Image Gallery"><img src="images/help/sharing-files/sharing-by-post/post-with-gallery.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Post with Image Gallery</div>
			</div>
		</li>
	</ol>

</div>